{
  "message": "feat(flywheel-clients): scaffold Flywheel ecosystem client package\n\nCreates a workspace package dedicated to \u201cexternal tool\u201d integrations in the Flywheel ecosystem.\n\nRationale\n- Gateway will integrate with multiple CLIs/services (Agent Mail MCP, bv, cass, cm, ubs, etc).\n- Keeping these adapters in a single package prevents the gateway/web apps from:\n  - shelling out directly\n  - embedding parsing logic in route handlers\n  - drifting into multiple incompatible wrapper styles\n\nWhat\u2019s included\n- `packages/flywheel-clients` workspace package skeleton + TS config.\n- Namespaced stubs for the planned integrations:\n  - `src/agentmail` (MCP Agent Mail client patterns)\n  - `src/bv` (bv \u201crobot-*\u201d outputs; no interactive TUI)\n  - `src/cass` (cass `--robot/--json` usage)\n  - `src/cm` (cass-memory `--json` usage)\n  - `src/scanner` (UBS scanner integration)\n\nNotes\n- These modules are placeholders only; real implementations should follow the strict non-interactive constraints:\n  - never run bare `bv`/`cass` (TUI)\n  - prefer `--robot-*` / `--json` for deterministic outputs\n- Actual command schemas/parsers should be introduced alongside their corresponding feature beads.",
